gov.nasa.arc.mct.abbreviation
Interface Abbreviations

public interface Abbreviations

Defines a data structure that represents the set of abbreviations available for words and phrases in a string.

Method Summary

getPhrases

java.util.List<java.lang.String> getPhrases()
Gets the phrases into which the original string has been divided as possible abbreviations were found. The phrases, in order, comprise all words of the original string.

Returns:
a list of phrases that can be abbreviated

getAbbreviations

java.util.List<java.lang.String> getAbbreviations(java.lang.String phrase)
Gets the available abbreviations for a phrase. The list is always nonempty, since the first element is the phrase unchanged.

Parameters:
phrase - the phrase to abbreviate, which may be a single word
Returns:
a list of possible abbreviations for the phrase
